org.miloss.fgsms.sdks

Class FgsmsSDK

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miloss.fgsms.sdks.FgsmsSDK

  • public class FgsmsSDK
extends Object
    This class is an over simplified SDK, it basically automates creating web service proxies for all of the FGSMS service endpoints from a configuration file and provides some wrappers for some of the mundane tasks that you may find yourself tackling.
    Author:
    AO
